<LP>
   NETWORK SYSTEMS Corp. (Minneapolis) -- Lyle D. Altman,
59-year-old president and chief executive officer of this
communications systems company, assumed the additional post
of chairman, succeeding Jim Thornton, 64, who remains a
member of the board. Network called the move part of its
succession plan.
